<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
<p>Okay im still real new to the shammy class.  Ive reached 12th lvl but my main is 30th so im not a newbie (totally).  Now i know were not good at soloing pre pet levels, but we all know it does and will happen when you have to solo.  Does anyone have the time to gimme a rundown on how we solo and at what spell levels any of it changes?  I know (for example) lvl 14 on you can do root n nuke.  But does this change at all at say lvl 19 or 24?  Some people would have me believe were decent at meleeing.  Im a bit doubtful on that part.  Experienced shammies please give me an idea how we solo and just how much i can/should melee.  Thank you for your time</p>
</FONT>
