Cannabilize/Regen is *not* a remedy for inadequate base wisdom.  The more base wisdom you have the less you need to canabilize.  The less you cannabilize the less downtime you have....simple logic.  If I have 140 base wis and the other guy has 115 base wis, the other guy is gonna need to cannabilize more and sit on his butt while his health regens.
