Bah you kids these days have it easy.. when i was a youngen I didnt know when my DoT's wore off because I didnt get a message saying 'your sicken spell has worn off' or nothin like that, and thats the way it was and we liked it.  I did actually kite using nukes at 14-19 in EK because of this lack of knowledge.  And we didnt have these new fangled zones in kunark to level up and oasis was much more crowded than it is now, but thats the way it was and we liked it.   At 19-24 we used to fight like mad over the aviak guard spawns in lake rathe and the hermit in SK and I still used nukes mostly and one dot because I didnt want to waste mana if i was cancelling out my dots and thats the way it was and we liked it you durn whippersnappers...  Back in my day, root used to drop sow and you could solo shaman orcs in everfrost and run away like a little girl if you started to lose, but we liked it.  After 9 you shouldnt have any troubles soloing most stuff until you get near 30, since you can always run away faster than the mobs.. dem durn druids didnt get no sow until 14 ha ha ha.  I didnt even use my slow spells until I got my wolf pet because I didnt realize how durn nifty they were, I probably could have leveled a lot faster if I had used drowsy and all dem spells.  And yes, you can solo ok after 50, I went from 51 to 52 in a couple of days killing dem blasted ice giants in everfrost and made a tidy profit too, just slowed it and ebolted it and meleed with pet until i went down some then rooted it with pet on it and backed off and watched pet until it was about half and called it off to superregen (chloro+ pet regen rocks, regrowth rocks harder) until root broke and let pet engage until i got root back up.. if i only had one giant spawn i'd use 2 or 3 ebolts, the 51 damage pets worked and lived the longest, if you dont have one or a 49 pt pet then get one when you have the mana.  I did get 1hb up a ways because der werent no durn cool spears for us that i could get before i was in 40's and when spear of fate came out and all dem new nice piercers I went and put 85 skill points into piercing and raised it up a bit more since then... us shaman dont get many spells to put pts into, i have also put in 20 pts or so into several trade skills and I still have 50 extra pts at 52.. sigh  anyway all dem new user interface features and dem kunark zones shure make it easy for you youngens.. but thats the way it was and we liked it.<P>Petey
